These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, zombie, sports
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, cricket, parkour
1. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person watching zombie movies##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Movie-Genre      | zombie | sports | mystery |
| Sport   | cricket     | volleyball    | parkour   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, white, amber
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball, basketball
1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who likes blue##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Color   | blue    | amber        | white |
| Sport     | volleyball | basketball | rowing         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, designer, manager
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid, daffodil
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the chef##1
2. the chef is between the person who growsorchid and the manager##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Job   | designer | chef     | manager |
| Flower        | orchid  | daffodil | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, chinese, japanese
City: hamburg, rome, hannover
1. the american is the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the japanese is between the person traveling to rome and the person traveling to hamburg##2
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Nationality   | chinese  | japanese     | american |
| City           | rome | hannover | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, may, june
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, thai, indonesian
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the indonesian##1
3. the italian is between the indonesian and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Birthday   | may | june     | january |
| Nationality     | indonesian    | italian | thai    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, purple, pink
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, mirinda
1. the person drinking sprite is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes red##2
2. the person who likes red is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Color   | red  | purple   | pink        |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | sprite | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different games are played: poker, billiard, whist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, adventure, sports
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person playing whist and the person watching adventure movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Game          | billiard  | poker  | whist |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | thriller | sports     |

