The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, april, september
1. the person driving the bike is the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the trike##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | trike   | tram  | bike  |
| Birthday   | august | april | september |

