.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-14::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, baccarat, dannemann
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, dog
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Cigar   | bongani | dannemann | baccarat |
| Pet     | snake    | goldfish    | dog |

