The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, freelancer, videographer
1. the coach is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the hamster##2
2. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the bird is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Pet   | bird | rabbit   | hamster   |
| Job         | videographer  | coach | freelancer |

