.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, azure, white
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, fantasy, musical
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes white and the person watching fantasy movies##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Color      | white | azure   | light-blue |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | western | fantasy   |

 